- Implemented area plots, e.g. the fill argument for scatter traces
- First implementation of BarTraces.  Required creation of an abstract 
  class Trace.  Promising.   

# 2026-04-22 
- X Axis label is now centered relative to the chart area.  
- Implemented the line argument for a ScatterTrace.  This allows lines with 
  various shapes: spline, hv.  Still need to implement vh.  A line can have 
  various dash types.  These dash types show correctly in the legend. 

